PHP SDK Overview The MyCloud API PHP SDK provides a complete PHP implementation of the client side the API. With the PHP SDK, you do not need to worry about any of the low level details of programming with the API. Connectivity, authentication, model objects, logging, and other supporting code is all provided for you. When working with the PHP SDK, you will work primarily with the API model objects.
